data.description: Welcome to this charming cottage home located on a corner lot in the highly sought-after Suwanee Station community, just a stone's throw away from Suwanee Town Center. This delightful residence combines the cozy charm of a cottage with the convenience of urban living, offering you the best of both worlds.  Situated on a spacious corner lot, this home offers a picturesque setting.  The home's design exudes cottage charm, with a welcoming front porch and architectural details that create a warm and inviting ambiance.  Inside, you'll find an open and bright layout with plenty of natural light, creating a cheerful and comfortable living environment.  The well-appointed kitchen features modern new stainless-steel appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast bar, making it a perfect space for both cooking and entertaining.  The living room is a cozy retreat with a fireplace, providing warmth and comfort on chilly evenings.  The cottage offers 3 spacious bedrooms, each designed to provide restful sleep and relaxation.  Living in Suwanee Station means you're just a short walk or bike ride away from Suwanee Town Center, with its vibrant shops, restaurants, parks, and community events.  Suwanee is known for its top-rated schools, making it an excellent choice for families.  Suwanee Station offers a range of community amenities, including swimming pool, tennis, pickle ball, playground for an inclusive lifestyle.  Convenient access to major highways makes commuting to work or exploring nearby attractions a breeze.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this charming cottage home on a corner lot, just steps away from Suwanee Town Center. Experience the perfect blend of cottage living and urban convenience in this idyllic community. Schedule a tour today and envision the countless memories waiting to be made in this delightful corner-lot cottage home.
